                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/givenchybaby/">red herring</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">感觉是越写越长越写越差，乾隆写了那么多本，各种无关痛痒的床戏出来迎合恶俗口味，雍正本就没太多写头，还是康熙相对更加写实精彩一些</p>
        </div>
    </li>

